text: Soze may refer the following people: *Keyser Söze, a fictional character and the main antagonist in the 1995 film The Usual Suspects *Jaja Soze, pseudonym of the British hiphop artist, street activist, and entrepreneur Elijah Kerr *Keyza Soze, pseudonym of the German record producer and composer Konrad Karkos
title: Soze (surname)
